  "text": "Concerning MMF, medetomidine induces hyperglycaemia, which could be lowered by adding midazolam in a cat model [CITATION_1] . Fentanyl passively increases the BG level by inhibiting glucose-stimulated insulin release, which was seen in rat pancreatic islet cells [CITATION_2] .",
